  "description": "A woman stands on a grassy hill overlooking a valley bathed in the warm light of a setting sun. She is middle-aged with shoulder-length brown hair, lightly smiling at the camera. She wears a light blue, loosely fitted shirt, a patterned scarf around her neck, and tan pants. Her hands are casually placed on her hips. The landscape behind her is a rolling valley filled with trees and vegetation, all illuminated by the golden hour light. The sun is positioned high in the sky, creating prominent sunbeams that radiate across the frame. The foreground is composed of dry, golden grass on the hillside.",
